@mflanaga  

If you give a spell flashback using [Señor Snappy](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=227676), it loses flashback when it leaves the stack (is cast, then exiled), so you cannot use [Runic Repetition](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Runic Repetition) unless the card has Flashback printed on the card. The ruling is here:  

*An effect that gives flashback to an instant or sorcery card in your graveyard stops applying once that card has left the stack. The card won't have flashback while exiled and can't be the target of Runic Repetition (unless it naturally has flashback).*
